{'reviews': [{'author_name': 'Emmanuel Martinez', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100145136322520373541/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKz65zRio_WCfXsCqrKoanki-Q8MhMYHV3R26uVj22AjN85Ig=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2', 'rating': 2, 'relative_time_description': '2 weeks ago', 'text': "Be careful if you're vegetarian, it's the second time they have given me the wrong order and I only find out when I get to work, too late to do anything about it.

It's unfortunate I have to make this review because when I get the right order they are a very good breakfast stop or lunch stop. The southwest and veggie are really good.", 'time': 1770479803, 'translated': False}, {'author_name': 'Nick Siskoff', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102948746274059124334/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvTi5ldewkWEs3madbxptp2W2ZqQba-euGrS60isBDOireUsoh=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2', 'rating': 3, 'relative_time_description': '2 months ago', 'text': 'Been going here for years. Definitely would have rated them 5 stars in the past but over the last several months I have been getting consistently undercooked food to the point I expect it more often than not now. Prices are great, portions are really good, and the quality was amazing. Definitely has gotten worse recently though unfortunately. I really like the chicken pot pie pasty for lunch and the southwest one for breakfast. If they end up improving on their quality and return to what they once were I’d happily give them 5 stars again. Still would recommend trying.', 'time': 1766085405, 'translated': False}, {'author_name': 'Darryl Fox', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109231476167069331030/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJoXXrlcB7aOEaTWw0XfYOaT-cCvRw60bmgvj4akQBRLOxLNg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': '3 weeks ago', 'text': "I've been getting their pasties for a couple of decades.  Hands down, the best pasties on the planet.  I've shared the veggie with several friends, and they all agree.  Service is always pleasant.  I highly recommend them", 'time': 1769459327, 'translated': False}, {'author_name': 'Tom Szelag', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108425340970108719334/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUg5mt2NxregXGVAL3Gk0lpkRjrAcIiNhRhnA0S3VmGFh20VlS1pw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': '8 months ago', 'text': 'This is a good spot! Small, simple, straightforward. Some good people working there. Good food and honestly a pretty good value especially with how everything seems to be getting expensive these days.

A half-sized portion is plenty for me as a light breakfast on the go. Full-sized is more of a meal.', 'time': 1748779563, 'translated': False}, {'author_name': 'Amelia Lee', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109132050199100394613/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzYdlhMxQH_etieanP3xFaf6hFz9N2yazbw3LZvPxjriRNT-0kOg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': '3 years ago', 'text': 'Delicious pastry that I discovered by accident. The service was super friendly and fast. I ordered a sausage pastry with hot sauce and found my new favorite fast food in the city. The pastry was still hot and delicious with its egg and cheese filling. This shop is a great spot for quick, tasty, and cheap food. Loved it and will be back!', 'time': 1662352667, 'translated': False}]}

{'reviews': [{'author_name': 'reuben fendt', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117352825209881911353/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIAttUhwGDKlEUbY_2ngeAn2KKS3Oo-8QJDXpMbjmu5kvFdvA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': 'a week ago', 'text': 'A focal point of downtown Madison dining. Exceptional noodles et el. They have an expansive menu which recently got even bigger with more cold noodle options which is exciting for the summer. Mr & Mrs Ruyi don’t ever miss! And if you still not sure the self-branded chopsticks tells you all the attention to detail they put it to their food.', 'time': 1770603407, 'translated': False}, {'author_name': 'S', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103377860711834636800/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLennz6fNFnelORkXOy7gTtDnYiFk0s_cuG1qRWESaWB453YQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': '6 months ago', 'text': "I loved my vegetable spicy hotpot with hand pulled noodles! I got the spiciest option and it was actually nice and spicy, but also still tolerable, perfect. The broth was savory and flavorful. It was a nice filling dinner. I'm Chinese American and grew up with my Chinese immigrant mom's home cooking, and the food tasted authentic to me :)

I got take out so can't speak to the atmosphere, but I ordered online and my order was ready when it said it would be.", 'time': 1753657920, 'translated': False}, {'author_name': 'T-REX', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115640241364076199102/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxUXwngymBbvsWgqp7RlBDCn1h4ZClh46cdYRTa7s8rCnBlXSc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': '9 months ago', 'text': 'Had a nice meal at Ruyi.   Never had hand pulled noodles and they were great.  Really good texture.  Got the spicy chicken and it brought some heat
Check them out for some tasty noodles.', 'time': 1747001183, 'translated': False}, {'author_name': 'Jana Gharia', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108722191733489423859/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXimmKYDb2T5t_uCMXmPsjs6ko0VruOqBkaEAchjfCd_hgEn10=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': '3 weeks ago', 'text': 'My favorite restaurant in Madison. Quality and fresh food (you literally see them pulling the noodles). Homey and cozy environment. I have enjoyed everything I have eaten here and it the place I recommend to everyone. You have to add the house-made chili oil-- it adds everything ', 'time': 1769809160, 'translated': False}, {'author_name': 'Stephanie Hwang Kroll', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104049315030151204082/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKC3oZ7nxRxK8IhYgVCy0f-PbcOkVkHn5xs667sVGWlO8N7r3I=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': '3 months ago', 'text': 'Fantastic noodles — we had the spicy beef and it totally hit the spot. Savory broth with perfectly chewy noodles and a level of spice that was just right.', 'time': 1762024425, 'translated': False}]}

{'reviews': [{'author_name': 'The Connonedrum', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117568771099654817623/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVF7R9PR4vlJJ73NDtmRkwOIdImxMUJf5vAAIJzBPtxVyP8uKRr_w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': 'a month ago', 'text': 'I went to Justveggiez with my wife and the food was excellent. My wife had the Portobello Burger and I had the vegan burger. We both had the fries and strawberry shakes. Both sandwiches were amazing. The atmosphere was super chill and clean with great music playing in the background. It is black owned and operated and we look forward to coming back again.', 'time': 1767211259, 'translated': False}, {'author_name': 'Maria Pangalos', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109511646575257986535/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVT07oNws5ZwH9Z85ZoP6WyIsm7A1KNZEzzXYAvjZA-Y5u7koo0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': '3 months ago', 'text': 'As a vegan passing through THE dairy state & someone who is really passionate about exploring a place through food, I felt like I was missing out (a rare feeling). This place offers a relief - vegan cheese curds! They were delicious. It was wonderful to see a nod to such a cultural classic that everyone can enjoy regardless of diet.', 'time': 1763488770, 'translated': False}, {'author_name': 'Itamar Zabari', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104927594070931924428/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFuwOS-Y7QOS0hcD7aGytJe4zgdbagvOdsS9neGLHkhKurB4Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': '4 months ago', 'text': 'Very nice staff (owners?)

Great food, lots to choose from and all looks tasty.

Highly recommended!', 'time': 1761252636, 'translated': False}, {'author_name': 'Emily Nordhaus', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101694155548350619017/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1a2_siqdhoWjjlaBzesWS7IuSIOpJgwNp2SRFB6XuziEQZPPJRw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': 'a year ago', 'text': 'I was super excited to try the vegetarian/vegan restaurant on state street and it FULLY lived up to all of my expectations. I got the Thai chix wrap, and it was delicious. The “chicken” had a great slightly spicy sauce that gave it great flavor. Don’t be scared off by the menu pictures, the food was truly amazing! Definitely recommend!', 'time': 1721869832, 'translated': False}, {'author_name': 'Elijah B', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118080207895721957740/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'original_language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWbY0_AO-MXu7qkKDAIWTV2kN5nbuaEHNLwnl0pNbpZPi6Fg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': '7 months ago', 'text': '10/10! As a vegan traveler it can be hard to find good food everywhere I go but boyyy when I tell you this place is THE place to go! I got the power bowl, vegan cheese curds, a samosa, fries, quinoa salad and mac&cheese to last me a few days. Everything was seasoned just right and all the sauces were phenomenal. Definitely recommend if you’re in the area!', 'time': 1753233011, 'translated': False}]}
